message.content:
You can buy life insurance in Mississippi from Southern Farm Bureau Life Insurance Company. They offer a range of life insurance products, including both permanent and term life insurance options. 

Southern Farm Bureau Life Insurance Company highlights its commitment to providing competitive products, superior customer support, and maintaining high ethical standards. 

For more information, you can contact them via the following:
- **Address**: 1401 Livingston Lane, Jackson, MS 39213
- **Phone**: Customer Service - 601-981-7422, Death Claims - 1-800-562-0919, Policy Service - 1-800-457-9611
- **Website**: [sfbli.com](https://www.sfbli.com)
